    <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock screensteps-wrapper--introduction screensteps-wrapper">
  <div id="text-content_03FA12E0-22E9-0135-3052-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If you can make a reply in an announcement, you may be able to like announcement replies in your course. </p>
<p>If the steps in this lesson do not match what is displayed in your course, learn how to <a href="/t5/Student-Guide/How-do-I-like-a-reply-in-a-course-announcement-in-Announcements/ta-p/478613" target="_blank">like a reply to an announcement in the Announcements Redesign interface</a>.</p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>The liking feature may be restricted to users with grading permissions (e.g. instructors and TAs). If you cannot like an announcement reply, this feature is not available to you.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_announcements" data-step-uuid="0ec339ac-1f5e-4e78-809c-96c811a1e045">
    <h2 id="open_announcements" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Announcements</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/744/227/original/21183fe8-0b94-4da5-84ca-7271ba621f32.png" srcset="" alt="Open Announcements" height="312" width="174">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_03FA43A0-22E9-0135-3054-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Announcements</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_announcement" data-step-uuid="789aac36-dde7-4aae-ac86-07dc73c34410">
    <h2 id="open_announcement" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Announcement</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/380/054/original/ea038ec8-4c29-4d36-a2aa-ebf29e47bd81.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/380/054/medium/ea038ec8-4c29-4d36-a2aa-ebf29e47bd81.png" srcset="" alt="Open Announcement" height="353" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_03FA7180-22E9-0135-3056-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the name of the announcement.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="like_announcement_reply" data-step-uuid="cc957921-dc46-4b9e-9473-081c0fb5fde2">
    <h2 id="like_announcement_reply" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Like Announcement Reply</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/365/752/original/4ae934f9-289c-409e-9fca-39366a0f17ff.png" srcset="" alt="Like Announcement Reply" height="734" width="664">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_03FAA4E0-22E9-0135-3058-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Locate the reply and click the <strong>Like </strong>icon.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
        <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-2" id="view_liked_reply" data-step-uuid="fe5cb2b8-513e-4628-b181-1c2557092738">
    <h3 id="view_liked_reply" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Liked Reply</h3>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/365/754/original/94d9c3f6-3c62-4aa1-baaa-3bb190ec9c2d.png" srcset="" alt="View Liked Reply" height="278" width="648">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_03FAD430-22E9-0135-305A-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>The Like icon will be highlighted, indicating you have liked the reply. </p>
<p>When a reply is liked, the Like icon will also display the total number of likes for all users in the announcement.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view_liking_restriction" data-step-uuid="b7b0eaef-cc79-4529-8119-37a16d2bcd61">
    <h2 id="view_liking_restriction" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Liking Restriction</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/365/748/original/4a855b01-f1d9-48ff-878d-192e6434d7f9.png" srcset="" alt="View Liking Restriction" height="316" width="653">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_03FB0640-22E9-0135-305C-22000AB760A3" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If your instructor has restricted the liking option to only users with grading permissions, you will not be able to see the Like icon or like your favorite replies. However, you can still see the total number of likes given to each reply.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>
					
				
			
			
			
				
			
			
			
			
			
			
